# xv6 Shared Memory Subsystem

This project extends xv6-riscv by implementing a shared memory subsystem.

## Implemented Features

* shmget()
* shmat()
* shmdt()
* Shared physical page mapping
* Reference counting
* Automatic cleanup on process exit

## Modified Files

* kernel/proc.h
* kernel/proc.c
* kernel/defs.h
* kernel/main.c
* kernel/syscall.h
* kernel/syscall.c
* kernel/shm.h
* kernel/shm.c
* user/user.h
* user/usys.pl
* user/writer.c
* user/reader.c
* Makefile

